author: By ANDREW TAYLOR Associated Press
title: Washington set to deliver $2.2 trillion virus rescue bill
description: WASHINGTON (AP) — With rare bipartisanship and speed, Washington is about to deliver massive, unprecedented legislation to speed help to individuals and businesses as the coronavirus pandemic takes a devastating toll on the U.S. economy and health care system.
